            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the fish is cooked through, add the<strong> </strong>juice of <strong>half</strong> your<strong> lime[s]</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>to the pan</p><p>Give everything a good stir – this is your <strong>basa tom kha soup</strong></p><p>Cut the<strong> remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person </p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1723544776378-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1723544776378-x400.jpg",
