            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1723544776378-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Discard the<strong> outer lemongrass layers</strong> from the <strong>lemongrass rice</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>basa tom kha soup</strong> in a bowl with the<strong> lemongrass rice</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>coriander leaves</strong>, <strong>chopped coriander stalks</strong> and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
